  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">You divert a malevolent spirit from the River of Souls to haunt your opponent’s armor. This spell must target a suit of light, heavy, or powered armor. The armor becomes cumbersome, reducing the wearer’s speed by 10 feet and AC by 1. It also rattles, hisses, and screeches, imposing a –4 penalty on Stealth checks.</p>",
